QuestData.Title: The Eternal Revenge
QuestData.Description:
<On the shelves there are hundreds of other phylacteries of varying shapes and sizes.
Many bear names - this one specifically has a etching with the name Mor'Bitan.
Lady Vashj would be interested in this phylactery.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the phylactery of Mor'Bitan back to Lady Vashj.

Objectives.Objective: Return Mor'Bitan's Phylactery to Lady Vashj
